I have witnessed some risky overtaking.

Name: Indian Ocean Road
Description: I regularly drive indian ocean road and I believe the road is good but lacks overtaking lanes between Lancelin and Jurien Bay.  Also signs need to be erected pointing out not to pull out from a side road in front of oncoming vehicles.  This has happened to me on many occasions and I have come close to having a serious accident on 3 occasions. Last Monday a car pulled out from Pinnacles in front of me and then turned off at Cervantes.  There was no one behind me!!
